            {
              "type": "heading2",
              "text": "The First Flagship of a Global Rollout",
              "spans": []
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "text": "The Hind Al-Oud Bas Mall flagship marked the beginning of a full rebranding journey, setting a new benchmark for luxury perfume retail. Designed as an immersive environment where architecture, scent, and storytelling converge, it became the first store in a global rollout that now extends across the UAE, GCC, Moscow, and London.",
              "spans": []
            }
          ]
